HOW TO INSTALL lcdemu
---------------------

1) Unpack the archive
   tar xfvz lcdemu-0.5.tar.gz
   or
   tar xfvI lcdemu-0.5.tar.bz2

2) cd lcdemu-0.5

3) edit the Makefile. Maybe you want to change DEVICE (default is /dev/lcd)

4) make

5) make install


HOW TO START lcdemu
-------------------

1) Start lcdproc
   lcdproc -l MtxOrb 

2) Start lcdemu
   lcdemu & 
   (use lcdemu --help for more information)
